---
title: CivicRecords AI — Records Request Lifecycle (v1.1+)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Req as Requester
    participant Clerk as Records Clerk
    participant Sys as CivicRecords AI
    participant AI as Local LLM<br/>(Ollama)
    participant Sup as Supervisor /<br/>City Attorney
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Req->>Clerk: submits open records request (email / form / counter)
    Clerk->>Sys: creates Request (status: received)
    Sys->>Audit: log: request_created

    Clerk->>Sys: Search documents (natural language query)
    Sys->>AI: embed query → hybrid search (semantic + keyword)
    AI-->>Sys: ranked results with citations
    Sys-->>Clerk: results + AI summary

    Clerk->>Sys: attach responsive documents to request
    Sys->>AI: scan documents for exemptions (PII / statutory keywords)
    AI-->>Sys: exemption flags (SSN, personnel, law enforcement, etc.)
    Sys-->>Clerk: flags for review

    loop For each exemption flag
        Clerk->>Sys: Accept flag (will redact/withhold) OR Reject flag (not exempt)
        Sys->>Audit: log: flag_reviewed (decision + reviewer)
    end

    Clerk->>AI: Generate Response Letter (optional)
    AI-->>Clerk: draft letter (labeled AI-generated)
    Clerk->>Sys: edit and save draft

    Clerk->>Sys: Submit for Review (status: drafted)
    Sys->>Sup: notification: request ready for review
    Sys->>Audit: log: submitted_for_review

    Sup->>Sys: review documents, flags, draft letter
    alt Approved
        Sup->>Sys: Approve (status: approved)
        Sys->>Audit: log: request_approved
        Clerk->>Req: deliver response
        Clerk->>Sys: Mark Fulfilled (status: fulfilled)
        Sys->>Audit: log: request_fulfilled
    else Revision required
        Sup->>Sys: Request Revision + review notes
        Sys->>Clerk: notification: revision requested
        Sys->>Audit: log: revision_requested
        Clerk->>Sys: make corrections, resubmit
    end
